{
  "texts": [
    "Convolutional filters and then a nonlinear activation function called ReLU make up every convolutional layer.",
    "The pooling layers are used to carry execute Max Pooling.",
    "Due to the presence of fully connected layers, the intake size is set.",
    "The intake dimension is typically stated as 224x224x3, however, because of padding, it actually comes out to be 227x227x3.",
    "There are 60 million elements in AlexNet in total."
  ]
}